{"tid":2140823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女友嫌我煩，係咪要分手了","createTime":"2020-08-05T08:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T09:22:12.000Z","uid":204047,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1d627096db538fd8e461911f4e656fb91ce9dc","tid":2140823,"uid":204047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"拍左半年，嘈得太多大家都好攰，一日一小吵三日一大吵，而家佢唔見都冇所謂，每次傾到一啲相處既問題佢就避，佢係一個完全唔迫得既人，一迫佢就會炆，有時佢會想自己一個人或者同朋友一齊 多過見到我，試過嘈到分手但係又氹得番<br />\n<br />\n但我唔搵佢 佢又會搵我，睇得出佢仲鍾意但係好攰，呢啲位應該點做？"},{"pid":"d2becd9e5f2b050c09f35b0d721843a3232039d4","tid":2140823,"uid":60307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"c1f165e128fc0d20fbab33337566f6409c4a3b91","tid":2140823,"uid":218737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:04.000Z","msg":"分啦"},{"pid":"e9a65d5b097cb121cb711da37642e5c3062cafb8","tid":2140823,"uid":302546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2becd9e5f2b050c09f35b0d721843a3232039d4","tid":2140823,"uid":60307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"分手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:08.000Z","msg":"要狠"},{"pid":"4a57de6e0064b08e9cccc651c115ccf772c73959","tid":2140823,"uid":271130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:14.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律建議分手"},{"pid":"8e57d4354d6987a86b5cbbc292b0d0eca52fdade","tid":2140823,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:19.000Z","msg":"嘈咩"},{"pid":"5218a5c0134d1aab5c9a23f11b186d518d13f728","tid":2140823,"uid":125731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"中出完好走"},{"pid":"2903d803ce4975719210e17a65191020c170ec28","tid":2140823,"uid":243179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03128b8276b5fa35df9805b